  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3466500/extras/d13a50651f4657fab1ca8d03ff672121.avif?t=1747760463\" width=616 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3466500/extras/a3b8d3031df7e928b36c435f273d043b.avif?t=1747760463\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3466500/extras_big/a3b8d3031df7e928b36c435f273d043b.avif?t=1747760463 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The stage is set when Lazriel awakes without any memories to call her own. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Awaiting her is Remi, a quiet young man whose gaze seems to pierce through her. Without anyone else to turn to, Lazriel finds herself under Remi's care.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3466500/extras/9edc451c25ff5f72c4acd1ebd7714268.avif?t=1747760463\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3466500/extras_big/9edc451c25ff5f72c4acd1ebd7714268.avif?t=1747760463 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, it becomes clear that there is much that Remi is hiding from her.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lazriel begins to harbor doubts—about Remi, about her own origins</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3466500/extras/d9c878ec594e054c23fc8f2ab0a3266b.avif?t=1747760463\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3466500/extras_big/d9c878ec594e054c23fc8f2ab0a3266b.avif?t=1747760463 width=800 height=1505 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But most importantly, about her nightmares where she becomes Ilsa, an unassuming village girl with a terrible fate lying in store.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lazriel's worries only worsen once rumors are soon abound that a malevolent witch lurks nearby.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will Lazriel discover who she is?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                        Can the cycle of tragedy that binds these actors be severed?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And what shall remain once the curtains fall: love, or a witch's curse?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3466500/extras/4334d31ef7a87fb1fb1906967b31213c.avif?t=1747760463\" width=616 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3466500/extras/7c283330cdc69aa983fd5e4b8bd30b8e.avif?t=1747760463\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3466500/extras_big/7c283330cdc69aa983fd5e4b8bd30b8e.avif?t=1747760463 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3466500/extras/e34ad5edb1275d2d877008a4036cf194.avif?t=1747760463\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3466500/extras_big/e34ad5edb1275d2d877008a4036cf194.avif?t=1747760463 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\